WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: the headline — stock tailscale clients joining our plane.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: the harness builds octravpn-node for linux containers.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.000
narrator: cargo build runs cold the first time; warm runs are seconds.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:30.000
narrator: each compile artifact lands in target/linux-debug.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:10.000
narrator: docker compose brings up mesh-control plus a derp sidecar.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:40.000
narrator: two stock tailscale peers boot, named tsi-peer-a and -b.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:10.000
narrator: the harness mints a preauth key via the CLI surface.

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:40.000
narrator: both peers run tailscale up against our control plane URL.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:10.000
narrator: the IP plane converges — peer-a and peer-b see each other.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:50.000
narrator: tailscale ping rides the encrypted WireGuard tunnel.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:30.000
narrator: the script asserts a successful ping round trip.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:06:00.000
narrator: exit zero — stock tailscale just paid an operator on Octra.
